This paper is about semantic image manipulation, which involves understanding and reasoning about the semantic concepts of images. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper discusses applications such as interactive image editing and data-driven image manipulation, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.AI, followed by cs.LG, cs.GR, and cs.MM.
